HEADWORD: Corrigent
<hw>Cor"ri*gent</hw> <pr>(k?r"r?--j<it>e</it>nt)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>corrigens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>corrigere</ets> to
